Omg real funny s*** lol love his comedy. You would to if you're a guy that's be in multiple relationships in past or present don't matter you'll laugh your a** off. Not so funny for the women, sorry ladies. Hope you can handle the truth.
Corey Holcomb is the funniest comedian after kevin hart of course.  You have to have a crazy way of thinking when listening to him.  Product was delivered on time.
After reading other reviews of this DVD, I had pretty high expectations. It was okay. I have seen him in other clips and he was hilarious. I still will support his work.
this dvd came extremely fast - and i'm very glad- this dvd is funny as all out. i highly recommend it to anyone who like to laugh - it's great.

Corey Holcomb is a great break from the usual styles you'll see out there. Noone else is like this guy. Very funny lines, very fresh approach to situations we have all been in. If you appreciate humor, and don't take the topics too serious ( an issue Corey deals with in this comedy skit) you will enjoy this very much.
